sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Database

    Client->>API: DELETE /carts/{cartId}
    API->>Database: SELECT id FROM carts WHERE id = $1
    Database-->>API: carts row (or not found)
    alt cart not found
        API-->>Client: 404 Not Found (ProblemDetail)
    else cart found
        API->>Database: DELETE FROM cart_items WHERE cart_id = $1
        API->>Database: DELETE FROM carts WHERE id = $1
        API-->>Client: 204 No Content
    end
